These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  analyst, pilot, accountant, bartender, scientist, manager, project-manager
There are 7 different nationalities: colombian, italian, pakistani, egyptian, brazilian, malaysian, russian
 1. the bartender is on the left of the egyptian##1
 2. the brazilian is the bartender##1
 3. the project-manager is on the right of the manager##1
 4. the pakistani is on the right of the malaysian##1
 5. the accountant is in the middle##1
 6. the colombian is on the far left##1
 7. the scientist is the colombian##1
 8. the analyst is on the right of the malaysian##1
 9. the pakistani is on the left of the italian##1
10. the egyptian is on the left of the accountant##1
11. the project-manager is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | scientist | bartender | pilot | accountant | analyst | manager | project-manager |
| Nationality   | colombian    | brazilian   | egyptian      | malaysian | pakistani    | italian    | russian         |

