.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: carrot, mango, banana, lime, potato, grapes, spinach
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: disco, reggae, jazz, hip-hop, country, folk, indie
 1. the fan of country is the person eating lime##1
 2. the person eating grapes is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 3. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating mango is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 5. the person eating lime is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 6. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 7. the fan of country is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of country is on the right of the person eating potato##1
 9. the fan of indie is on the left of the person eating banana##1
10. the person eating lime is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | carrot | mango | potato | lime | grapes | spinach | banana |
| Music-Genre   | reggae      | jazz   | hip-hop   | country      | disco       | indie       | folk     |

