.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: papaya, kiwi, nectarine, artichoke, watermelon, lime, garlic
The people have 7 different jobs:  paramedic, security-guard, accountant, coach, police-officer, engineer, nurse
 1. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the nurse##1
 3. the security-guard is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
 4. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 5. the paramedic is the person eating watermelon##1
 6. the accountant is on the right of the security-guard##1
 7. the security-guard is on the left of the accountant##1
 8. the security-guard is on the right of the coach##1
 9. the person eating lime is the coach##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the paramedic##1
11. the coach is in the middle##1
12. the person eating garlic is on the left of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | kiwi | watermelon     | nectarine  | lime       | papaya       | garlic  | artichoke   |
| Job    | engineer  | paramedic | nurse | coach | security-guard | accountant | police-officer |

