.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, salsa, dubstep, pop, classical, techno, gospel
There are 7 different nationalities: american, pakistani, canadian, turkish, dutch, french, chinese
 1. the fan of classical is the pakistani##1
 2. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 3. the french is on the right of the canadian##1
 4. the american is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 6. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
 7. the canadian is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the french##1
 9. the fan of dubstep is the dutch##1
10. the dutch is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
11. the chinese is the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | gospel     | pop     | dubstep      | salsa | classical      | electronic     |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian | french | dutch | chinese | pakistani | american |

