.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: chess, woodworking, writing, traveling, collecting, filmmaking, skydiving
7 different pets are kept: pony, turtle, cat, rabbit, hedgehog, ferret, lizard
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the owner of the ferret is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | woodworking | writing | filmmaking     | traveling | skydiving | collecting | chess |
| Pet     | lizard   | cat    | hedgehog | ferret     | pony         | rabbit     | turtle        |

