.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, fanta, tea, mirinda, milk, water
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, train, motorbike, snowmobile, airplane, taxi, bike
 1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 2. the person drinking cola is the person driving the car##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | fanta | milk   | cola | tea | water  | mirinda | hot-chocolate |
| Transport   | snowmobile   | airplane | car | taxi     | train | bike | motorbike   |

