.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: horror, fantasy, documentary, action, thriller, western, superhero
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, ship, bus, car, van, quad-bike, bike
 1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is the person driving the car##1
 4. the person driving the van is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror  | superhero | action | thriller | western     | fantasy | documentary |
| Transport     | quad-bike | car      | bike | bus    | van | ship   | airplane  |

