The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: spy, horror, satire, epic, mystery, thriller, time-travel
 1. the person watching horror movies is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |    7     |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | board-games   | writing | skydiving | cooking | woodworking | video-games  |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | mystery | time-travel  | satire | thriller | spy     | horror |

